trans-unit.source: Find out how you can expand your business opportunities and become a Microsoft partner and Business Central reseller.

seg-source.mrk: Find out how you can expand your business opportunities and become a Microsoft partner and Business Central reseller.

target.mrk: Zjistěte, jak můžete rozšířit své obchodní příležitosti a stát se partnerem společnosti Microsoft a distributorem produktu Business Central.

trans-unit.source: If you specialize in Cloud solutions, Office 365, SharePoint, industry solutions, analytics, ERP, CRM, accounting software, and/or business process optimization software/services, Business Central is a new opportunity.

seg-source.mrk: If you specialize in Cloud solutions, Office 365, SharePoint, industry solutions, analytics, ERP, CRM, accounting software, and/or business process optimization software/services, Business Central is a new opportunity.

target.mrk: Pokud se specializujete na cloudová řešení, Office 365, SharePoint, průmyslová řešení, analytiku, ERP, CRM, účetní software nebo software/služby pro optimalizaci podnikových procesů, Business Central je nová příležitost.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] can help you differentiate and deepen customer relationships by giving you the capability to deliver an end-to-end business management solution that’s connecting people and processes like never before, embedded within familiar Microsoft Office tools that small and medium businesses use every day.
